Parliament, Monday, 12 March 2018 –The Portfolio Committee on Public Enterprises tasked with the inquiry into the mismanagement of state funds in state-owned enterprises will tomorrow hear evidence from the Minister of Home Affairs, Mr Malusi Gigaba, former South African Airways Chairperson Ms Dudu Myeni and the Gupta brothers and associates. Details of the inquiry: Date : Tuesday, 13 March 2018
	Time : 09:30
	Venue : Good Hope Chamber ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Yoliswa Landu
